+    reason: Its no-transcript-in-Sinex boundary conflicts with the transcript-complete backed-mode target.
+  - work_item: polylogue-fs1.9
+    reason: Re-scope its low-volume events as notifications, correlation summaries, lag, and health signals rather than the storage boundary.
