+  - stable refs survive parser replay and material resegmentation
+  - incomplete revision bundles never appear complete
+  - a clean SQLite projection rebuilds from Sinex with explained parity
+  - accepted assertions, judgments, and context deliveries survive that rebuild
+  - physical deletion invalidates server projections, SQLite replicas, FTS, vectors, context artifacts, and model effects
